modName: Lost Hideout Of Zal Mel Fur
summary: This is the Ancient Hideout of Zal Mel Fur...
descriptionHtml:
This is the Ancient Hideout of Zal Mel Fur...

This is my personal hideout in Skyrim.

Features:

A small room filled with: 

9 (Nine) Storage chests
Weapon racks
Shield racks
1 (One) Enchanting workbench
1 (One) Blacksmith workbench
1 (One) Throne
1 (One) Double bed
1 (One) Ancient Dragon Altar and 2 Locked chests...If you like really small practical Hideouts/Rooms then this is for you! (The room is also minor flooded with water cause its old)

This is my \"First Edition\" Release! \"Second Edition\" will come in the future and will feature more rooms with objects and details etc. =)
author: DarkIncLegion
